Command to create a new directory: 
    mkdir directory_name
    by adding a parents flag -p it is possible to create a directories with hierarchy
      mkdir -p dir1/dir2/dir3

Command to see a directory contents:
    ls   
    Flags can be added to this command:
       -l    to see a detailed view of files and directories
       -a    to see hidden files and directories 
       -h    to see a human readable file sizes
       
Command to remove a directory:
    rm -r dir1 
    to remove without deleting permition request -f flag can be added
  
